I see this type of request in my office pretty often. A customer calls or writes in with a proposal that looks almost like this: &ldquo;I have my servers running in us-east-1, all behind a load balancer. Can you assist us with a failover setup in the us-west-1 region?&rdquo;
Yes, I most certainly can, but it probably isn&rsquo;t what you want.
You run multiple EC2 instances, behind a load balancer or two.
